1. *Eksperimenti* su pokazali da je nova metoda efikasnija od prethodne. (Experiments have shown that the new method is more efficient than the previous one.)
2. U školi smo radili *eksperiment* o kretanju tijela u slobodnom padu. (We did an experiment in school about the motion of objects in free fall.)
3. *Eksperimentalni* program će se sprovoditi u narednih nekoliko mjeseci. (The experimental program will be implemented in the next few months.)
4. Naš profesor bi uvijek isticao važnost *eksperimentalnog* pristupa u nauci. (Our professor would always emphasize the importance of the experimental approach in science.)
5. *Eksperimentisanje* sa opasnim hemikalijama može biti veoma rizično. (Experimenting with dangerous chemicals can be very risky.)
6. Ova studija se fokusira na *eksperimentalnu* primjenu nove tehnologije. (This study focuses on the experimental application of new technology.)
7. Na kraju *eksperimenta* dobili smo očekivane rezultate. (At the end of the experiment, we got the expected results.)
8. Da bismo potvrdili hipotezu, moramo sprovesti više *eksperimenata*. (To confirm the hypothesis, we need to conduct more experiments.)
9. *Eksperimentisanje* sa novim ukusima hrane postaje sve popularnije. (Experimenting with new food flavors is becoming more and more popular.)
10. Tim istraživača je uspješno realizovao *eksperimentalni* projekat. (The team of researchers successfully implemented an experimental project.)